name: Kimjor #3 I'm Tiger, Momm.
description:
Welcome to the world of Kim Jor. A mischievous little Forpus who loves to travel around in his mother's dreamland.

This is the first NFT in KimJor Roadmap. You will get beautiful images in a variety of styles with the purple forpus is hidden.  Yes, he is Mr.Kim Jor. 
Enjoy in my cute dreamland.

This piece is designed to welcome the upcoming Year of the Tiger. The green letters reflect the Year of the Tree Conservation. And there is a clover to show good luck to everyone. Happy New Year.
